  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help us build the Playground in the Cloud, an inspiring and fun open online platform to build and nurture a community around SOLE. People can share, talk, play, learn together and connect communities all over Colombia, especially people most affected by the armed conflict. We want to change education and empower communities in Colombia with SOLE, invented by TED Prize winner Sugata Mitra. His vision was to build the School in the Cloud, we want to turn it up with our Playground!</narrative>
  </description>
